alt_text:
This is a character concept art of a young woman in a blocky body type.
She has some sort of crop top with sleeves rolled up. A necklace can be noticed, showing a shark tooth. A piece of blue fabric is tied around her arm. She has a wide overalls with one unattached side, under which can be seen a pair of pants with a belt. On the same side, a fish net is attached to the belt. She is also barefoot.
On the side of the character, her haircut is shown from the back, revealing a brown loose braid with a red rubber band to hold it off.

Some text can be read on the right side of the picture:
Alcyone; Important figure in Avendale; Renown fisherwoman
-Fierce, courageous
-Isn't afraid to roll up her sleeves
